{"thig13.1:0.1":"Therigatha 13.1 ","thig13.1:0.2":"Visatinipata ","thig13.1:0.3":"Ambapalitherigatha ","thig13.1:1.1":"“Kalaka bhamaravannasadisa, ","thig13.1:1.2":"Vellitagga mama muddhaja ahum; ","thig13.1:1.3":"Te jaraya sanavakasadisa, ","thig13.1:1.4":"Saccavadivacanam anannatha. ","thig13.1:2.1":"Vasitova surabhi karandako, ","thig13.1:2.2":"Pupphapura mama uttamangajo; ","thig13.1:2.3":"Tam jarayatha salomagandhikam, ","thig13.1:2.4":"Saccavadivacanam anannatha. ","thig13.1:3.1":"Kananamva sahitam suropitam, ","thig13.1:3.2":"Kocchasucivicitaggasobhitam; ","thig13.1:3.3":"Tam jaraya viralam tahim tahim, ","thig13.1:3.4":"Saccavadivacanam anannatha. ","thig13.1:4.1":"Kanhakhandhakasuvannamanditam, ","thig13.1:4.2":"Sobhate suvenihilankatam; ","thig13.1:4.3":"Tam jaraya khalitam siram katam, ","thig13.1:4.4":"Saccavadivacanam anannatha. ","thig13.1:5.1":"Cittakarasukatava lekhika, ","thig13.1:5.2":"Sobhare su bhamuka pure mama; ","thig13.1:5.3":"Ta jaraya valibhippalambita, ","thig13.1:5.4":"Saccavadivacanam anannatha. ","thig13.1:6.1":"Bhassara surucira yatha mani, ","thig13.1:6.2":"Nettahesumabhinilamayata; ","thig13.1:6.3":"Te jarayabhihata na sobhare, ","thig13.1:6.4":"Saccavadivacanam anannatha. ","thig13.1:7.1":"Sanhatungasadisi ca nasika, ","thig13.1:7.2":"Sobhate su abhiyobbanam pati; ","thig13.1:7.3":"Sa jaraya upakulita viya, ","thig13.1:7.4":"Saccavadivacanam anannatha. ","thig13.1:8.1":"Kankanamva sukatam sunitthitam, ","thig13.1:8.2":"Sobhare su mama kannapaliyo; ","thig13.1:8.3":"Ta jaraya valibhippalambita, ","thig13.1:8.4":"Saccavadivacanam anannatha. ","thig13.1:9.1":"Pattalimakulavannasadisa, ","thig13.1:9.2":"Sobhare su danta pure mama; ","thig13.1:9.3":"Te jaraya khandita casita, ","thig13.1:9.4":"Saccavadivacanam anannatha. ","thig13.1:10.1":"Kananamhi vanasandacarini, ","thig13.1:10.2":"Kokilava madhuram nikujiham; ","thig13.1:10.3":"Tam jaraya khalitam tahim tahim, ","thig13.1:10.4":"Saccavadivacanam anannatha. ","thig13.1:11.1":"Sanhakamburiva suppamajjita, ","thig13.1:11.2":"Sobhate su giva pure mama; ","thig13.1:11.3":"Sa jaraya bhagga vinamita, ","thig13.1:11.4":"Saccavadivacanam anannatha. ","thig13.1:12.1":"Vattapalighasadisopama ubho, ","thig13.1:12.2":"Sobhare su baha pure mama; ","thig13.1:12.3":"Ta jaraya yatha patalibbalita, ","thig13.1:12.4":"Saccavadivacanam anannatha. ","thig13.1:13.1":"Sanhamuddikasuvannamandita, ","thig13.1:13.2":"Sobhare su hattha pure mama; ","thig13.1:13.3":"Te jaraya yatha mulamulika, ","thig13.1:13.4":"Saccavadivacanam anannatha. ","thig13.1:14.1":"Pinavattasahituggata ubho, ","thig13.1:14.2":"Sobhare su thanaka pure mama; ","thig13.1:14.3":"Thevikiva lambanti nodaka, ","thig13.1:14.4":"Saccavadivacanam anannatha. ","thig13.1:15.1":"Kancanassa phalakamva sammattham, ","thig13.1:15.2":"Sobhate su kayo pure mama; ","thig13.1:15.3":"So valihi sukhumahi otato, ","thig13.1:15.4":"Saccavadivacanam anannatha. ","thig13.1:16.1":"Nagabhogasadisopama ubho, ","thig13.1:16.2":"Sobhare su uru pure mama; ","thig13.1:16.3":"Te jaraya yatha velunaliyo, ","thig13.1:16.4":"Saccavadivacanam anannatha. ","thig13.1:17.1":"Sanhanupurasuvannamandita, ","thig13.1:17.2":"Sobhare su jangha pure mama; ","thig13.1:17.3":"Ta jaraya tiladandakariva, ","thig13.1:17.4":"Saccavadivacanam anannatha. ","thig13.1:18.1":"Tulapunnasadisopama ubho, ","thig13.1:18.2":"Sobhare su pada pure mama; ","thig13.1:18.3":"Te jaraya phutita valimata, ","thig13.1:18.4":"Saccavadivacanam anannatha. ","thig13.1:19.1":"Ediso ahu ayam samussayo, ","thig13.1:19.2":"Jajjaro bahudukkhanamalayo; ","thig13.1:19.3":"Sopalepapatito jaragharo, ","thig13.1:19.4":"Saccavadivacanam anannatha”. ","thig13.1:20.1":"… Ambapali theri …. "}